Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:18.90,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:21.16,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Did Uroko-sama just fart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:23.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are farts\N all you ever hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:24.03,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:24.92,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:27.50,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,We heard about Akari-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:29.09,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:36.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:13.02,Episode-Title - Copy,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3: The Tradition of the Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:24.20,Thank you,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Namiji Junior High
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.29,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,There's saltflake snow \Neven in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:34.92,Entrance Ceremony,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.92,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Hayakawa is always so nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:34.91,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he seem so scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:37.53,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,They were talking about \Nthe rules of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:41.22,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,There might be some reason \Nthat people get banished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This is all Akari's guy's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:47.73,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But he seemed nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:50.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki, your taste in guys sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.44,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't that the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.23,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:57.08,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this, I'm going \Nto find out everything about this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And if he's an asshole, \NI'm going to punch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:01.49,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,And if he ends up being a decent guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.15,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll punch him gently!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:05.34,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,V-Violence is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:08.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's his fault for putting his hands on a \Ngirl from the sea when he's from the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:09.98,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:11.91,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid girls go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:14.88,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This is now a guys-only planning meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:16.87,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:17.73,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.59,Music Room,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Music Room
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:30.52,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Hikari calms down a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:33.00,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,He's impossible when he's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:35.98,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.90,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-chan! A sea slug!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:42.97,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's one with a red belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:47.62,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell a red-bellied sea slug about \Nfeelings you can't tell anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:51.69,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,it'll tell you what's going \Nto happen in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:54.69,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if it spits up a black rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:57.04,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,your feelings are wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.09,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,and if it spits up a pretty rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:04.01,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,...those feelings will continue to \Nshine on forever like a jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:08.35,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:12.10,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Tsumugu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.66,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.28,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Chii-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.03,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll do this tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.95,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this will even work though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.59,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That car had a fishery \Ncooperative mark, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he tried to run...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.39,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But if I like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:37.84,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'd want \Nto go out with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.88,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,If I went out with him, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:46.04,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,maybe we'd kiss like Akari-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.18,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I'm a pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.18,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:56.06,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:04:59.81,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,And if I thought about getting married,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:03.49,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I wouldn't be \Nable to come back here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:06.80,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to think about that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.17,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You're not even sure if \Nyou like him yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:10.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.62,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But I like you, and Hii-kun and Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.71,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:17.21,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But Tsu—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.71,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little different \Nwith Kihara-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.43,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:25.31,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:28.50,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.25,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We're going home, Manaka, Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.68,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.88,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You're done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:38.27,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was faster than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:42.85,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That night...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.84,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.15,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.62,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad and Akari acted \Nlike they usually do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:54.91,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and didn't say a word about anything \Nthat happened at Uroko-sama's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.12,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:59.12,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:04.37,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All throughout the night, \NI could hear soft, soft, crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.44,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,There were two nights like this up until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:15.64,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I used to call Akari "Nee-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:19.98,Flashback,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Sea that's full of compassion, waves \Nthat flutter, the bright light...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:22.56,Flashback,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The sea that nurtures all life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:26.38,Flashback,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The turning storm, \Nthe tide that takes all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:30.53,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mom! Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:28.69,Flashback,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The abyss that opens Agito...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:34.18,Flashback,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The master of the sea, Sea God, \Nthe exalted one I am born from,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:37.71,Flashback,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,save the soul of Sakishima Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:39.11,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:44.52,Flashback,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Guide her soul along with the \Nsacred fire to where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:42.17,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She didn't cry at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:49.09,Flashback,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Let us praise all of the good \Nshe did in this life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.36,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:58.05,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that it was weird that she
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:01.91,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,was acting like an adult and wasn't \Ncrying even though she was a kid too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.46,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.86,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.57,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.10,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.99,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to start working \Nat Oshiooshi's Saya Mart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:16.65,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! You said you wanted \Nto be a manga artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.94,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That you were going to go to \Nschool for it on the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:23.57,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but they said they'd let \Nme draw the signs at the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:26.96,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally going to create a famous \Nmascot and bring in the sales!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:29.59,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap, Akari! \NStop trying to gloss things over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:35.76,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough money for \Nboth of us to go to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:39.50,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't plan on going to college! But you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.56,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:44.28,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You might change your mind once \Nyou're in high school, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.62,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't even go to high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:47.97,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I hate studying anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:54.36,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wha— L-Let me go, Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:58.01,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:05.06,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing changed with me \Ncalling Nee-chan "Akari."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:08.98,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What I called her didn't \Nchange anything between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:16.68,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I realized it was my fault that she\Nwas becoming an adult more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:22.24,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pissed off at her guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:26.48,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't really understand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:29.94,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but I was sort of relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:36.07,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,About the fact that Akari finally \Nstarted thinking about herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.33,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:41.44,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,And if I thought about getting married,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:45.12,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,388}I wonder if I wouldn't be \Nable to come back here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:49.50,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I was frustrated about Manaka too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:53.03,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But I knew that Manaka was \Nprobably even more frustrated...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:59.79,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,About the people on the surface \Nand the people of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:06.31,fishing_cooperative,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.51,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:13.71,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're not going to start \Npunching out of nowhere, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:14.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:17.10,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk for a while and then I'll\Nlook for an opening to punch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:19.20,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:21.16,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:25.75,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:30.39,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:31.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.63,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we made plans with \Nhim, so it can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:36.01,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.20,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.07,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.57,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hikari... How far did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:01.60,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.12,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:11.19,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara-kun's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:17.79,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,So that'll be the shipping\Ndate starting next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:18.72,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.43,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:21.22,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.18,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wouldn't\Nstart suddenly punching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:23.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:28.50,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you, old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:36.53,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,These eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.74,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,They're a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:42.20,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.06,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:43.74,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:47.79,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari? Are you Akari's younger brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.75,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:50.34,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:52.25,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari's crying because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:55.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And all the old guys of Shioshishio \Nare on her case because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.36,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.91,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,You there. The girl didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:01.52,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:05.29,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an ordinary thing \Nfor a person from the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.89,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,and a person from the \Nsea to get together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:08.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:10.79,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:15.40,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's the rivalry, as well as the \Nissue with fishing grounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.90,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.53,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.28,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to have babies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.32,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:25.49,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Is this old man senile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.08,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That's the problem, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:31.08,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:41.99,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The biggest difference between the people \Non the surface and the people of the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.38,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,is the Ena that covers \Nthe people of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:50.11,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Ena is similar to the amnion \Nthat covers the fetus,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:53.81,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,and the people on the surface break \Nthrough this when they're born.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:59.28,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,But the people of the sea are born \Nwith this being a part of their skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.72,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Just like scales on a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:07.95,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The people of the sea are able to \Nbreathe underwater because they have Ena...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:15.04,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,A child born between a person from \Nthe surface and a person from the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:16.92,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,is born without Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:22.35,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then if Akari-san had a baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.98,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,That baby wouldn't be able \Nto live in the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:27.22,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.09,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,That means there'd be \Nfewer descendants...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:32.13,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,That's why if you marry \Nsomeone from the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:33.89,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,you're banished from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.77,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Banished from the village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:37.27,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:40.98,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't Akari tell me anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:42.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:44.61,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me, Hikari-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:48.20,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not messing around with Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:53.20,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then do you plan\Non marrying Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:55.30,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:13:00.25,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're dating her but you have \Nno plans to take responsibility?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:01.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.73,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:03.62,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:07.05,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really remember \Nwhat happened after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:11.06,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,He kept taking punches \Nfrom me for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.08,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.18,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and when I realized it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:27.73,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:33.14,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.46,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends went to soak in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.32,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You need to keep wet, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:42.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's surprising if you\Ndo that all of the sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:45.00,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I always wondered what \Nhappened to your clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:47.13,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,when you come up to \Nthe surface all wet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:49.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,When we're on dry land,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:52.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,apparently the Ena sucks up any \Nextra moisture and stores it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.14,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.30,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.63,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this earlier too,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:03.90,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but how do you know so \Nmuch about Shioshishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.40,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Because I think it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:08.49,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you why you \Nthink it's grea—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.87,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:13.03,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get some more water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:16.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about it. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:17.46,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.99,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get up too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.22,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara Tsumugu is a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:39.96,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that early on, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:41.76,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.05,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:46.39,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who threw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:51.78,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess it's weird \Nfor me to thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.48,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Ena...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:04.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, are you from Shioshishio—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.71,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:08.58,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.85,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:17.27,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you got thrown around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:22.02,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Did that guy contact you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.11,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:26.28,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari! Give up on that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:27.87,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally not—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:29.06,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:29.99,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:34.24,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't have worked \Nout with him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:37.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you're giving up that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.26,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:39.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:42.72,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You can worry about the baby \Nwhen you actually have one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:46.96,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're supposed to learn that in \Nhealth class your third year in junior high...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.37,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,but you already found out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:51.60,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.31,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,People on the surface \Nand people of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:57.93,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn't be together anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:15:59.81,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.01,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:05.06,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, there are only a few \Nsingle guys in the village, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:08.20,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,So getting married is pretty hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.70,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,How can you laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:17.33,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I'll just have \Nto resort to forbidden love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari! Stop messing around! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:21.41,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:23.27,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:30.71,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:34.26,Main,kids,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:36.86,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Kihara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:37.72,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.91,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.12,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.49,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:45.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu, thanks for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:48.42,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:52.57,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was trying really hard \Nnot to call him by his first name!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.65,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You said that it was \Nperverted if I did, Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:57.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine if it's between guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:58.16,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:00.94,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then I'll call him that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:01.72,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.85,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no fair, Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:06.75,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going to do it too! \NIt's okay, right, Tsumugu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:09.42,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:12.23,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:13.42,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.38,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:19.45,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you and Tsumugu-kun \Nare a little closer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:21.43,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're calling him Tsumugu, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:25.00,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Tsumugu-kun is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:28.54,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking he'd be able to be \Nfriends with you someday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:31.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You really do worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.78,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:38.75,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry. I didn't mean \Nto act all mature again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:51.71,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you \Nworry all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:57.96,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to be more mature, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:59.40,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:01.93,Wood Shop Room,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Wood Shop Room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.92,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're making good progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:05.85,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:09.60,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys keep it up, \Nyou'll be done soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:10.73,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:14.10,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Since you did so well, I'll \Ntreat you guys to some ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:20.74,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to treat \Nmy students to ramen one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:23.54,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:25.39,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I want miso ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:27.25,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.98,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost five...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:32.41,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:34.53,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Then next time—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.19,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.33,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:48.04,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu-kun was making this for us so \Nwe could get work done at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.27,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.77,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the fish might \Nwant to breathe, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.74,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.05,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.28,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Manaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:05.01,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:06.31,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.04,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.51,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I was lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:13.40,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:18.99,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Your curse was lifted?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:19.82,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:22.75,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But... if Uroko-sama curses me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:25.18,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that was a curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.53,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Because I threw some food at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.79,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Though he didn't curse\Nme again last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:32.71,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,If I try to do something bad again, \Nhe'll probably do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.26,0:19:35.52,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:41.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka... what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:43.37,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impersonating the fish from the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:44.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:45.29,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:07.68,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:10.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:14.19,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:16.81,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:21.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:41.03,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Um... what about the ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.16,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You really do dry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.60,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But you're all soaked, Tsumugu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:56.53,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:21:00.42,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot that I had\Nto stop by some place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:01.59,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:02.74,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:18.86,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:24.28,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But on TV, they lost \Nconsciousness after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.43,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:27.90,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You need to soak it with \Nchloroform to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:29.93,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's not going to work \Nwith just a handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:32.62,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,The damn media got me dancing to their tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.71,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, dancing like an octopus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:38.35,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You're the octopus, octopus-head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:39.29,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:42.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What? If you're her friend, do \Nsomething about this idiot—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:43.95,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:44.69,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:48.82,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Help me break up my dad and that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:57.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,D...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:59.15,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:33.07,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,That's a rather blunt\Ncriminal declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:34.78,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep this between us, Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:36.22,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:37.22,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the only bad guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:39.73,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.10,Episode-Title - Copy,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4: Because We're Friends
